                <head>No. 82.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Morton</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Frelinghuysen</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1883-12-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">December</hi> 29, 1883</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>It was stated in Chamber that Dr. Dettmar, who was charged by American Government
                    to investigate trichinosis question, advised in his official report that all the
                    hogs of the districts where trichinae had made its appearance should be
                    destroyed. Important to be fully informed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>MORTON.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
